 class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> 的**<code>matchMedia()</code>** 方法返回一个新的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a> 对象，表示指定的<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">媒体查询 (en-US)</a>字符串解析后的结果。返回的<code>MediaQueryList</code> 可被用于判定<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Document\"><code>Document</code></a>是否匹配媒体查询，或者监控一个<code>document</code> 来判定它匹配了或者停止匹配了此媒体查询。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">mqList = window.matchMedia(mediaQueryString)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"mediaquerystring\"><code>mediaQueryString</code></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>一个被用于媒体查询解析的字符串。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p>一个用来媒体查询的新的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a>对象</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"使用说明","title":"使用说明","isH3":false,"content":"<p>您可以使用返回的媒体查询来执行即时检查和事件驱动检查，以查看文档是否与媒体查询匹配。</p>\n<p>要执行一次瞬时检查以查看文档是否与媒体查询匹配，请查看<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/matches\" title=\"matches\"><code>matches</code></a>属性的值，当 document 满足媒体查询条件的时候将会返回<code>true</code>。</p>\n<p>如果您需要始终了解 document 是否与媒体查询匹配，则可以查看将要传递给对象的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/change_event\" title=\"change\"><code>change</code></a> 事件 。<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/devicePixelRatio\"><code>Window.devicePixelRatio</code></a>上的文章中有一个很好的例子。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"举例","title":"举例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>此示例运行媒体查询<code>(max-width: 600px)</code>并在<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/HTML/Element/span\"><code>&lt;span&gt;</code></a>;中显示<code>MediaQueryList</code>的<code>matches</code>属性值。如果视口的宽度小于或等于 600 像素，则输出将为 true，而如果窗口的宽度大于此宽度，则将输出 false。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"javascript","title":"JavaScript","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"notranslate\">let mql = window.matchMedia('(max-width: 600px)');\n\ndocument.querySelector(\".mq-value\").innerText = mql.matches;\n</pre>\n<p>JavaScript 代码只需将要匹配的媒体查询字符串传递到<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia\" title=\"matchMedia()\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>matchMedia()</code></a>进行编译，然后设置<code>&lt;span&gt;</code>的<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement/innerText\" title=\"innerText\"><code>innerText</code></a>为<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList/media\"><code>matches</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>属性结果的值，以便它表明此 document 在此刻页面加载完成时是否与媒体查询所匹配。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"html","title":"HTML","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>span</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>mq-value<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>span</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>一个简单的 <code>&lt;span&gt;</code> 来接收输出。</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: css hidden notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">.mq-value</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 18px arial<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-weight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> bold<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #88f<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.4em<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">border</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 1px solid #dde<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"result","title":"Result","isH3":true,"content":"<iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"举例\" id=\"frame_examples\" width=\"100%\" height=\"60\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia/_sample_.examples.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe>\n<p>参考更多的例子来 <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通过代码使用媒体查询 (en-US)</a> 。</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.csswg.org/cssom-view/#dom-window-matchmedia","title":"CSSOM View Module"}],"query":"api.Window.matchMedia"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.matchMedia","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"请参阅","title":"请参阅","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Using_media_queries\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">媒体查询 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Media_Queries/Testing_media_queries\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">通过代码使用媒体查询 (en-US)</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryList</code></a></li>\n  <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaQueryList\"><code>MediaQueryListListener</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"使用说明","id":"使用说明"},{"text":"举例","id":"举例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"请参阅","id":"请参阅"}],"summary":"Window 的**matchMedia()** 方法返回一个新的MediaQueryList 对象，表示指定的媒体查询 (en-US)字符串解析后的结果。返回的MediaQueryList 可被用于判定Document是否匹配媒体查询，或者监控一个document 来判定它匹配了或者停止匹配了此媒体查询。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.matchMedia","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"window.matchMedia","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Window.matchMedia()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/matchmedia","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/matchmedia/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/matchMedia","title":"Window.matchMedia()"}],"pageTitle":"Window.matchMedia() - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}